%% Diagram: Pull (Prometheus) vs push (OTLP) collection sequencing
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant SD as Service discovery
    participant App as Service / target
    participant Coll as OTel Collector
    participant TSDB as TSDB / backend

    Note over Prom,TSDB: Pull model
    Prom->>SD: list targets
    SD-->>Prom: target set
    loop every scrape_interval (15-60 s)
        Prom->>App: GET /metrics
        App-->>Prom: text exposition (200 OK)
        Note over Prom: emit up{job="..."}=1
        Prom->>TSDB: append samples
    end

    Note over Prom,TSDB: Push model
    loop on flush interval / event
        App->>Coll: OTLP gRPC export (metrics, logs, spans)
        Coll-->>App: ack
        Coll->>TSDB: forward (batched, possibly tail-sampled)
    end
    Note over App,Coll: target health needs separate signal<br/>(heartbeat, sidecar liveness)
